Package: rusdm
Type: Package
Title: Access Data from the US Drought Monitor API
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person('Nicholas', 'Potter', email='econpotter@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
  ) 
Maintainer: Nicholas Potter <econpotter@gmail.com>
Description: Interface to access data via the United States Drought Monitor's 
  web API <https://droughtmonitor.unl.edu/DmData/DataDownload/WebServiceInfo.aspx>. 
  Convenience functions facilitate building queries based on available 
  parameters and valid parameter values. This product uses the NASS API but is 
  not endorsed or certified by the US Drought Monitor.
URL: https://docs.ropensci.org/rnassqs/ (website)
     https://github.com/potterzot/rusdm/
BugReports: https://github.com/potterzot/usdm/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Language: en-US
